{"tid":2223782,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人成日食肉都覺得啲肉有陣臭味","createTime":"2020-09-30T05:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T10:48:09.000Z","uid":221696,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"78a06c8e58209a5f72565abccf5e12fd1860181f","tid":2223782,"uid":221696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:34:44.000Z","msg":"頭先茶記食乾炒牛河，夾咗件牛肉食之後好想反胃。<br />\n有時候打邊爐食嘅豬牛雞，我都會覺得肉味好重，但屋企人同朋友都話啲肉無味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n羊肉更加唔洗講，由細到大都唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟係啲肉唔靚定係我有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9572a9fbad6065e4e072009d6c7d733912f3dbc9","tid":2223782,"uid":65473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:41:35.000Z","msg":"試吓中一次武肺<br />\n好大機會會好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee902d5b06cf0a9052498dd65848010eedd5c0f0","tid":2223782,"uid":3649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"同我好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我本身唔係太好肉，但又未到話完全唔食，<br />\n出街都唔會避開肉類，<br />\n不過嗰餐冇乜肉都唔會投訴嗰類人<br />\n<br />\n肉淨係食豬牛雞，<br />\n海鮮一樣唔係太好，好少食。<br />\n肉食最鍾意雞肉，<br />\n不過有時都會突然頂唔順雞肉浸味，<br />\n我都唔知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cd58d86d204a9c88695ee294c2d1bd546ff3d9","tid":2223782,"uid":221696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee902d5b06cf0a9052498dd65848010eedd5c0f0","tid":2223782,"uid":3649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"同我好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我本身唔係太好肉，但又未到話完全唔食，<br />\n出街都唔會避開肉類，<br />\n不過嗰餐冇乜肉都唔會投訴嗰類人<br />\n<br />\n肉淨係食豬牛雞，<br />\n海鮮一樣唔係太好，好少食。<br />\n肉食最鍾意雞肉，<br />\n不過有時都會突然頂唔順雞肉浸味，<br />\n我都唔知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"